{"tid":760114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杭州豆腐渣廊橋塌頂　8死3傷","createTime":"2018-07-29T08:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T01:28:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4dece718e44580b7eef8f9d1d0317527a8ea2b45","tid":760114,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180729/20463066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463066&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=425a9c24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463066&h=4c0667ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180729/20463066</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月29日 <br />\n<br />\n杭州豆腐渣廊橋塌頂　8死3傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180729/large/29cx06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F29cx06p.jpg&h=fb6030d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■杭州市廊橋的橋頂不敵風雨，瞬間倒塌，釀成8死3傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n浙江省杭州市桐廬縣合村鄉前晚廊橋的橋頂發生倒塌，造成8死3傷。目擊者指，當時天氣惡劣，出現狂風暴雨，「雨一來，風一來，橋就倒掉了」。事發時有人在橋上乘涼，有人則在避雨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180729/large/a1103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180729%2Flarge%2Fa1103a.gif&h=987271bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■廊橋原貌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20多人徒手挖掘救人<br />\n<br />\n氣象資料雖顯示，事發時當地受強對流天氣影響，持續刮起近20分鐘的大風，並伴有雷電和降雨。事發橋樑的基座為雙拱橋，建造於1984年，但廊橋是2016年公開招標建造的，不排除與工程質量有關。<br />\n<br />\n工程負責人已被相關部門控制，等候進一步調查結果。村民方金友表示，事發前晚7時40分，初時他也在廊橋內，因下雨趕回家，不料半分鐘後廊橋就倒塌了。他趕往現場與其他一起救人，把被壓的人搬出來，「搬起來以後（發現）橋底還有活的人，還有活人在底下」。另一村民方樟德表示，他看見橋上有人被木頭壓在身上，「全部我們村子裏的」。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員丁增梁表示趕到場時，發現原來挺漂亮的一個廊坊全塌了，差不多全部人都掉下去了，沒多久大家就衝上去徒手挖掘，20多人一字排開，直接趟水過去幫忙拯救：「不知道水下有沒有人&hellip;&hellip;大概半個小時，就有六個人被挖出來。」經過1個多小時搜救，有11人被救出，但其中8人失救死亡。死者包括三男五女，年紀最輕的49歲，最大的74歲。3名傷者則沒有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n浙江之聲/中新網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中證監改制　長生生物恐除牌<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n台女童被狗追　疑受驚嚇猝死"},{"pid":"278b74b46a998a27db7ceddd3debb172c9fad01d","tid":760114,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":17,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.jiuwa.net/tuku/20171009/7yWKBIZe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiuwa.net%2Ftuku%2F20171009%2F7yWKBIZe.jpg&h=9d35e38b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b9009275b6b0028a4a3f53dbc213df235413c93","tid":760114,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港豬澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc89c2658be024b0983b1a707e36b8475144e074","tid":760114,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"#2我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5521c77e13b735e379088bb56f6a29a65821981e","tid":760114,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3579f8e418d24b0de5045ef87daf370f5a6100c8","tid":760114,"uid":54060,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"條橋質量完全無問題<br />\n肯撚定係千年一遇嘅大雨怪風<br />\n甚至係萬年先至咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64e3514e1cfd61407ca1e37091aa0eaad73d655","tid":760114,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy